---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const meta = {
  title: '10Web AI Website Builder Review: WordPress-Powered AI Builder',
  description: '10Web uses AI to generate WordPress websites. Create sites in minutes. WordPress-based with hosting included. $10/month for basic plan. Best for WordPress users who want AI assistance.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['10Web review', '10Web AI', 'WordPress AI builder', '10Web pricing', 'AI website generator'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4285F4]/5 to-[#34A853]/5 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#4285F4] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        AI Tool Review · 2025 Updated
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        10Web AI Website Builder Review
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        10Web generates WordPress websites using AI. You describe what you want, it creates a WordPress site. Hosting included. $10/month for personal plan. Best if you want WordPress specifically, not just any website.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-[#4285F4]/10 border-2 border-[#4285F4] rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick verdict: 10Web is excellent if you want WordPress with AI assistance. You get the power of WordPress (plugins, themes, ecosystem) with AI-generated content and design. Not as fast as Durable or as easy as Framer, but more flexible. Best for WordPress users who want to speed up site creation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What 10Web Is -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What 10Web Actually Is
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">10Web is:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>AI website builder:</strong> Generate WordPress sites from prompts</li>
          <li>• <strong>WordPress-based:</strong> Uses WordPress as the platform</li>
          <li>• <strong>Hosting included:</strong> Managed WordPress hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI assistant:</strong> Generates content, images, and design</li>
          <li>• <strong>Page builder:</strong> Elementor-based editing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What makes 10Web different:</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Unlike Durable or Framer, 10Web generates WordPress sites:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Full WordPress ecosystem (50,000+ plugins)</li>
          <li>• SEO power (WordPress is SEO-friendly)</li>
          <li>• Content management (WordPress is best for CMS)</li>
          <li>• Ecommerce (WooCommerce integration)</li>
          <li>• Extensible (add any functionality via plugins)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Tradeoff:</strong> More complex than drag-and-drop builders. Steeper learning curve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How 10Web Works -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      How 10Web Works
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Step 1: Describe your website</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Tell 10Web what you want: "coffee shop in Seattle with online ordering" or "personal blog for tech reviews."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Step 2: AI generates your site</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">10Web creates a WordPress site with pages, content, and images based on your description. Takes 1-2 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Step 3: Customize with Elementor</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Edit the generated site using Elementor page builder. Drag-and-drop interface to tweak design, add content, change layout.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Step 4: Publish</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Your site is hosted on 10Web's managed WordPress hosting. Custom domain included on paid plans. Live in minutes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What 10Web is Good At -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What 10Web is Good At
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. WordPress Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">10Web's biggest strength is WordPress:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Full WordPress:</strong> Not a limited platform, real WordPress</li>
          <li>• <strong>Plugin ecosystem:</strong> 50,000+ plugins available</li>
          <li>• <strong>Theme flexibility:</strong> Change themes anytime</li>
          <li>• <strong>WooCommerce:</strong> Full ecommerce capability</li>
          <li>• <strong>SEO power:</strong> WordPress + Yoast/RankMath</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Benefit:</strong> You're not locked into a proprietary platform. WordPress is yours to customize.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. AI Content Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">10Web's AI generates decent content:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Page copy:</strong> Writes text for your pages</li>
          <li>• <strong>Blogging:</strong> Generates blog post drafts</li>
          <li>• <strong>Product descriptions:</strong> Ecommerce content</li>
          <li>• <strong>Images:</strong> Suggests relevant images</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Quality:</strong> Better than blank slate, needs human editing for quality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Managed WordPress Hosting</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hosting is included and managed:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Fast servers:</strong> Google Cloud hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>Automatic updates:</strong> WordPress core updates handled</li>
          <li>• <strong>Daily backups:</strong> Automatic backups included</li>
          <li>• <strong>Security:</strong> Malware scanning and protection</li>
          <li>• <strong>SSL certificates:</strong> Free SSL on all plans</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Benefit:</strong> Don't need separate hosting. Everything included.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Elementor Page Builder</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Edit with Elementor (industry standard):</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Drag-and-drop:</strong> Visual editing interface</li>
          <li>• <strong>Widgets:</strong> Hundreds of pre-built elements</li>
          <li>• <strong>Templates:</strong> Start from pre-made designs</li>
          <li>• <strong>Responsive:</strong> Mobile editing built-in</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Benefit:</strong> Elementor is powerful and widely used. Tutorials available everywhere.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">5. Speed and Performance</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Sites load fast on 10Web:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Google Cloud:</strong> Premium hosting infrastructure</li>
          <li>• <strong>CDN included:</strong> Cloudflare integration</li>
          <li>• <strong>Caching:</strong> Built-in caching system</li>
          <li>• <strong>Image optimization:</strong> Automatic image compression</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Result:</strong> Good performance scores out of the box.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What 10Web is Bad At -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What 10Web is Bad At
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. Not Beginner-Friendly</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">WordPress has learning curve:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• WordPress concepts to learn (posts, pages, themes, plugins)</li>
          <li>• Elementor has its own interface</li>
          <li>• More complex than Durable or Framer</li>
          <li>• Requires some technical comfort</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Not for you if:</strong> You want simplest possible solution. Consider Framer or Durable instead.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. AI Quality is Average</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">AI generation is decent, not amazing:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Design is functional, not stunning</li>
          <li>• Content needs editing (not publication-ready)</li>
          <li>• Images are stock, not custom</li>
          <li>• Less "wow" factor than competitors</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Reality:</strong> Good starting point, but you'll customize heavily.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Plugin Bloat</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">WordPress can get bloated:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• Too many plugins slows site</li>
          <li>• Plugin conflicts break things</li>
          <li>• Need plugin management discipline</li>
          <li>• Security updates required</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Tradeoff:</strong> Flexibility vs. simplicity. More plugins = more complexity.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Pricing Adds Up</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Base price is just the start:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• $10/month for basic plan</li>
          <li>• Premium themes cost extra</li>
          <li>• Premium plugins cost extra</li>
          <li>• Higher plans needed for more sites</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Comparison:</strong> Durable and Framer include everything in one price.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">5. Slower Than Dedicated Builders</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">AI generation is slower:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• 10Web: 1-2 minutes to generate</li>
          <li>• Durable: 30 seconds to generate</li>
          <li>• Framer: Import templates instantly</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why:</strong> WordPress is heavier than purpose-built builders.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      10Web Pricing
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Personal: $10/month (billed annually)</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• 1 website</li>
          <li>• 10GB storage</li>
          <li>• AI website builder</li>
          <li>• Elementor Pro included ($59/year value)</li>
          <li>• SSL certificate</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Premium: $20/month (billed annually)</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• 3 websites</li>
          <li>• 20GB storage</li>
          <li>• Everything in Personal</li>
          <li>• Priority support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold mb-3">Agency: $60/month (billed annually)</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• 10 websites</li>
          <li>• 40GB storage</li>
          <li>• Everything in Premium</li>
          <li>• White labeling</li>
          <li>• Client billing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      When to Use 10Web
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Perfect for:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>WordPress users:</strong> Who want AI-assisted site creation</li>
          <li>• <strong>Bloggers:</strong> Who want WordPress's blogging power</li>
          <li>• <strong>Ecommerce:</strong> Who want WooCommerce</li>
          <li>• <strong>Agencies:</strong> Building WordPress sites for clients</li>
          <li>• <strong>People comfortable with tech:</strong> Willing to learn WordPress</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Not for:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Beginners:</strong> Who want simplest solution</li>
          <li>• <strong>Non-tech users:</strong> Uncomfortable learning new systems</li>
          <li>• <strong>Simple sites:</strong> Landing pages work better on Framer</li>
          <li>• <strong>Service businesses:</strong> Durable is faster/easier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      10Web vs Competitors
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold"></th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">10Web</th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Durable</th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Framer</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Platform</td>
            <td class="p-4">WordPress</td>
            <td class="p-4">Proprietary</td>
            <td class="p-4">Proprietary</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Learning curve</td>
            <td class="p-4">Medium</td>
            <td class="p-4">Very easy</td>
            <td class="p-4">Easy</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Flexibility</td>
            <td class="p-4">Very high</td>
            <td class="p-4">Medium</td>
            <td class="p-4">High</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Ecommerce</td>
            <td class="p-4">WooCommerce</td>
            <td class="p-4">Basic</td>
            <td class="p-4">Via Stripe</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Plugin ecosystem</td>
            <td class="p-4">50,000+ plugins</td>
            <td class="p-4">Limited</td>
            <td class="p-4">Integrations</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Starting price</td>
            <td class="p-4">$10/mo</td>
            <td class="p-4">$15/mo</td>
            <td class="p-4">$16/mo</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-[#4285F4]/10 border-2 border-[#4285F4] rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">10Web is the right choice if you specifically want WordPress with AI assistance. You get WordPress's power and ecosystem with AI-generated content and design. Not the simplest or fastest, but most flexible.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Choose 10Web if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You know you want WordPress</li>
        <li>• You need WooCommerce for ecommerce</li>
        <li>• You value plugin ecosystem</li>
        <li>• You're comfortable learning WordPress</li>
        <li>• You want AI to speed up WordPress setup</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Choose Durable if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You want the absolute easiest AI builder</li>
        <li>• You're a service business</li>
        <li>• You need a site in 30 seconds</li>
        <li>• You're non-technical</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Choose Framer if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li>• You want beautiful design easily</li>
        <li>• You're a designer or care about aesthetics</li>
        <li>• You need portfolio/landing page</li>
        <li>• You want something simpler than WordPress</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related AI Tool Reviews
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/durable-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable AI Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Easiest AI website builder</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/v0-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">v0.dev Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI code generator by Vercel</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
